03.02.2025 - Throwback

3 Years, Countless Memories & A Lifetime to Go… 🎢❤️”

“Three years ago, I wasn’t looking for love, yet love found me in the most unexpected way—wrapped in friendship, laughter, and endless debates over the silliest things. Cut to today, and here we are: still ranting, still bickering, still holding onto each other through every high and every low.

This journey hasn’t been picture-perfect—because let’s be real, we’re more ‘chaos and comfort’ than ‘sugar and spice.’ But through every setback, every eye-roll, and every tight hug that made it all worth it, we’ve nurtured something real. We’re not just partners, we’re each other’s safe place, each other’s home.

So here’s to 3 years of love, of growing, of becoming way too comfortable (maybe a little too much, but oh well 😉). 

Shared this late, but love doesn’t run on deadlines, does it? 💖
 #3YearsOfUs #perfectlyimperfect❤️ #FoundLoveWhenILeastExpectedIt #AndStillBickering #throwbackcelebration #coupleofkahaniyaan
